TOKENS:
Characters: a-z|A-Z
DIGIT: 0-9
PERIOD: .
Operators: times|plus|minus|divided by

Grammar:
PROGRAM : PROGRAM SENTENCE | SENTENCE
SENTENCE::= EXPRESSION | DEFINITION | QUESTION
EXPRESSION : EXPRESSION plus TERM | EXPRESSION minus TERM | TERM
TERM : TERM times FACTOR | TERM divided by FACTOR | FACTOR
DEFINITION::= IDENTIFIER is a ENTITY | IDENTIFIER is an ENTITY| IDENTIFIER are LIST
QUESTION::= is ENTITY BOOL ? | is ENTITY a DATATYPE ? | are LIST ENTITY ? | are ENTITY a DATATYPE ? | what is ENTITY ?
ENTITY : IDENTIFIER | DATATYPE
DATATYPE : NUMBER | BOOL | LIST
LIST : ENTITY , LIST | ENTITY
FACTOR : NUMBER
NUMBER::= Digit+
BOOL::= true | false
IDENTIFIER::= Characters{Characters|Digit}*
